&gt; I would like to do the following
&gt; - Run a TestCase #1
&gt; - Get the result from TestCase #1
&gt; - Run TestCase #2 using the result of TestCase #1

It&#39;s not good practice to have tests dependent on each other.  I suggest you
add code to TestCase #2 to retrieve the results you need so you have
something like this:

test1() {
    Result1 result = getStuff();
    checkResult1(result);
}

test2() {
    Result1 result1 = getStuff();
    Result2 result2 = getOtherStuff(result1);
    checkResult2(result2);
}

